<h2><%= @booker.name.presence || "A Bookify user" %> invited you to Bookify</h2>

<p>You've been invited to join Bookify so you can get paid for your work.</p>

<p>Here's what happens next:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Click the button below to accept the invitation</li>
  <li>Verify your identity through Payout Partner (takes ~5 minutes)</li>
  <li>You're set up and ready to get paid!</li>
</ol>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 24px 0;">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #0D9488; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 24px;">
      <a href="<%= @invitation_url %>" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">Accept Invitation</a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px;">
  Or copy this link: <%= @invitation_url %>
</p>

<p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px;">
  If you have questions, contact <%= @booker.name.presence || "the person who invited you" %> directly.
</p>
